                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-45-off259 t18180401-45-crimeloc262"></join>. The copper was in my shop for sale on the 2d of March, between ten and eleven o'clock in the morning. I was fetched down stairs, found the prisoner in custody, and the copper by his side. I am in partnership with John Sutherland.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180401-45-person344">
                  JOHN 
                  JONES
               <interp inst="t18180401-45-person344" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
